Cura is a mobile phone application based on the Android platform.
It is a bundle of remote systems administration tools targeted mainly at sysadmins.

When in the hands of a sysadmin, Cura will provide:
 Personal terminal emulator with full Bash (bourne-again
shell) capabilities. Along with ready-made commands a
button away (ssh, top, uname, uptime, cat /proc/cpuinfo,
dmidecode, etc..)

 Access to the most powerful port/vulnerability-scanning
and penetration-testing tools (Nessus, Nmap, Wireshark).

 Machine log-monitoring featuring Geo-location and log-to-
SMS subscription capabilities.

 Personal communication/sharing space between colleagues.
